---
layout: base.njk
title: Vile u Banji Vrujci — Smeštaj sa lux apartmanima
description: "Pregled svih vila u Banji Vrujci — Vila Sofija, Jelena, Iva, Ema, Elipsa, Aqua Casa i druge. Filtrirajte po udaljenosti od bazena i kapacitetu."
permalink: /smestaj/vile/
activeNav: smestaj
breadcrumbs:
  - { label: "Početna", url: "/" }
  - { label: "Smeštaj", url: "/smestaj" }
  - { label: "Vile", url: null }
---
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-head">
    <div class="eyebrow">Smeštaj · Banja Vrujci</div>
    <h1>Vile u Banji Vrujci</h1>
    <p>Vile u Banji Vrujci nude razne pogodnosti — neke u svom sastavu imaju restoran i nude usluge pansiona ili polupansiona, druge su poznate po blizini bazena i mirnoj lokaciji u centru banje. Pregledajte svih {{ collections.vile.length }} vila i izaberite onu koja najviše odgovara vašem odmoru.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="filter-bar">
    <div class="chip-row" id="chipRow">
      <button class="chip active" data-filter="all">Sve vile</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="dist" data-max="250">≤ 250m od bazena</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="dist" data-max="500">≤ 500m od bazena</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="cap" data-min="6">6+ osoba</button>
      <button class="chip" data-filter="restoran">Sa restoranom</button>
    </div>
    <select class="sort-select" id="sortSelect">
      <option value="default">Preporučeno</option>
      <option value="distance">Najbliže bazenima</option>
      <option value="capacity">Najveći kapacitet</option>
      <option value="name">Naziv A–Š</option>
    </select>
  </div>
  <div class="results-count" id="resultsCount">Prikazano <b>{{ collections.vile.length }}</b> od <b>{{ collections.vile.length }}</b> vila</div>

  <div class="listing-grid" id="listingGrid">
    {% for item in collections.vile %}
    {% set c = item.data.card %}
    <div class="list-card"
       data-distance="{{ c.distance if c else 9999 }}"
       data-capacity="{{ c.capacity if c else 0 }}"
       data-restoran="{{ '1' if c.restoran else '0' }}"
       data-name="{{ item.data.title }}">
      <a class="lc-overlay" href="{{ item.url | noslash }}" aria-label="{{ item.data.title }}"></a>
      <div class="lc-thumb">
        {% if c and c.badge %}<span class="lc-badge">{{ c.badge }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% if c and c.price %}<span class="lc-price">{{ c.price }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% if item.data.slike and item.data.slike[0] %}
        <img src="{{ item.data.slike[0] }}" alt="{{ item.data.title }}" onerror="this.style.opacity=0">
        {% else %}
        <span class="lc-mono">{{ item.data.title | first }}</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="lc-body">
        <h3>{{ item.data.title }}</h3>
        {% if c and c.rating %}<div class="lc-stars">★★★★★ <span>{{ c.rating }}{% if c.reviews %} ({{ c.reviews }}){% endif %}</span></div>{% endif %}
        {% if c and c.desc %}<p>{{ c.desc }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if c and c.tags and c.tags.length %}
        <div class="lc-tags">{% for tag in c.tags %}<span class="lc-tag">{{ tag }}</span>{% endfor %}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="lc-footer">
          {% if item.data.telefon %}{% set phone = item.data.telefon %}{% include "partials/contact-icons.njk" %}{% else %}<span class="lc-call">📞 Pozovite za broj</span>{% endif %}
          <span class="lc-link">Detalji →</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="no-results" id="noResults">Nema vila koje odgovaraju izabranim filterima. <a href="#" onclick="resetListingFilters();return false;" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Resetuj filtere</a></div>

  <div class="load-more-wrap">
    <button class="load-more-btn" id="loadMoreBtn">Učitaj još smeštaja</button>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Vile u Banji Vrujci",
  "url": "https://www.banjavrujci.biz/smestaj/vile",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for item in collections.vile %}
      {"@type":"ListItem","position":{{ loop.index }},"name":"{{ item.data.title }}","url":"https://www.banjavrujci.biz{{ item.url | noslash }}"}{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
